column1: # There are two versions of the 1930s sheet, identical except for some months in 1940. The p270 copy seems to be from the 1960s and has been omitted.
# On the original 1930s sheet (p271) some of the readings for 1940 have been substantially adjusted (adding 3.5 inches in total).
# The adjustments seem to have been made by reference to Driffield Council School values.
# In February 1955 the gauge move to the Woodman's Cottage site.
